    "name": "Strangler",
    "steam_appid": 3249320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249320/extras/72ede132420472d83a276f0e9cf04b79.poster.avif?t=1737884046\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249320/extras/72ede132420472d83a276f0e9cf04b79.webm?t=1737884046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249320/extras/72ede132420472d83a276f0e9cf04b79.mp4?t=1737884046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hunt. Strangle. Eat! </strong>In this thrilling twist on classic Snake gameplay, you are the ultimate predator! Hunt, strangle, and devour your prey to grow and dominate the arena. Use cunning tactics and swift movements to control the space and outsmart your targets—not just in single-player but also in the intense VS mode, where you face off against player-controlled rats. Watch your tail as the rats can bite back! Each successful hunt hones your skills, but beware: lurking predators are eager to take you down. Do you have what it takes to become the biggest predator alive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249320/extras/89c70f0bdc2f98a192f0ecfe08ebcb7b.poster.avif?t=1737884046\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249320/extras/89c70f0bdc2f98a192f0ecfe08ebcb7b.webm?t=1737884046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249320/extras/89c70f0bdc2f98a192f0ecfe08ebcb7b.mp4?t=1737884046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                                    </strong>   <strong>Design Philosophy</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beautiful Minimalism</strong>: Easy to learn, hard to master. Experience simple rules that give rise to deep and engaging gameplay.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Risk-Reward Balance</strong>: Small mistakes result in minor setbacks rather than instant death, maintaining flow and allowing players to learn and improve. Larger lapses in attention, however, can lead to significant consequences, ensuring the stakes stay high.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable Difficulty:</strong> Fine-tune settings like speed, level size, and slither mode to create a challenge that fits your playstyle, from beginner to Snake-Fu master.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dual Role Design        </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>    </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249320/extras/3bba21cd1e3517e0f774ecc506387c4c.avif?t=1737884046\" width=120 height=112 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Size as a Disadvantage</strong>: Like in classic Snake, growing longer can make maneuvering more challenging.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Size as an Advantage</strong>: Use your increased size to your benefit by easily trapping prey, turning a potential weakness into a powerful asset.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lurking Predators as a Disadvantage</strong>: They can steal your food or even a piece of you, forcing you to maneuver carefully around them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lurking Predators as an Advantage</strong>: They can limit the mobility of prey by instilling fear, making it easier for you to trap and capture them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul></li></ul>",
